<plot>The Atlas Mountains is a film about Helen Thomas, an unhappily married woman, while spending Christmas alone at home, forms a brief yet passionate relationship with Tarik El Bez, a quiet immigrant worker who comes to fix her computer on a cold December night. Trapped in a small living room, the two loners find themselves engaging in a gentle struggle between intimacy and privacy.</plot><url>http://localhost:8983/solr/movie.html?541147</url></doc>
